{"tid":1043036,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[你們的女神] 靠朱晨麗傳情回氣　何廣沛密密操做肌佬","createTime":"2019-03-02T03:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T05:19:00.000Z","uid":12558,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"17b0f04afa03a4ca805a4db68f2c5d38e66d94a3","tid":1043036,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:18:41.000Z","msg":"飛躍進步男藝人何廣沛向來予人斯文形象，去年底他在台慶夜和丁子朗、張振朗鬥手瓜吋數，結果爆冷勝出，其實他已開始低調操肌，希望打造猛男形象。最近他透露將會到陽光與海灘之地拍攝旅遊節目《3日2夜》，「限奶令」後已甚少索女穿泳衣上陣，反而男藝人可攞正牌半裸騷肌，廣沛已預了晒成果，近日懷着破釜沉舟的心態狂操！ <br />\n<br />\n日前廣沛現身健身中心，起初他坐埋一邊密密食，連飯盒都是清淡雞肉，食到苦口苦面，即使好友兼教練李日昇撩他傾偈都冇乜反應。正式做Gym時，當日他主力操胸肌，做了多個器械訓練，十多分鐘後已開始咬牙切齒，但依然繼續奮戰兼且愈舉愈重，完成了十多組運動的廣沛開始面青青，但此時另一位教練Roy才出場幫廣沛操練手瓜，見他擰擰頭後再度踏上征途。再經過半小時狂舉，廣沛對麒麟臂谷到勁粗壯，相信不少女Fans望完都會覺得「嗒得杯落」，但精力耗盡的他要坐低回氣，見他仍不忘玩手機覆Message，未知是否向緋聞女友朱晨麗匯報成果。 <br />\n<br />\n令人眼前一亮 <br />\n<br />\n事後廣沛接受電話訪問時透露跟大隻佬郭子豪及李日昇操肌，目標是令人眼前一亮：「節目監製冇同我講要我準備啲咩，但我覺得操定先一定冇死。（目標要幾大隻？）冇追求數字上，係希望可以畀觀眾眼前一亮、脫胎換骨嘅感覺！（練習過程最辛苦係咩？）邊拍劇邊抽時間做Gym，同埋大時大節都要戒口，食得好清，全靠子豪同日昇幫我呢個可能連呼吸都唔識運用嘅新手，糾正我錯誤姿勢。」問到朱晨麗對他有何期望？他只笑言身邊很多同事覺得他要吃健康飯盒好慘，但都很支持及鼓勵他。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/111803_c63e5eb30927365fe2178672d697230f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F111803_c63e5eb30927365fe2178672d697230f.png&h=9eb72556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/111805_4157c238be828443efa5fbc5c3b13d2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F111805_4157c238be828443efa5fbc5c3b13d2c.png&h=897812cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/111807_613c6e7a61a693ef41f7608f8431826b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F111807_613c6e7a61a693ef41f7608f8431826b.png&h=75185269&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/111809_11a350e16018c4085a0ba90283984fb3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F111809_11a350e16018c4085a0ba90283984fb3.png&h=238759c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/111811_010f47480e7f15cc90cd7fab95a03412.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F111811_010f47480e7f15cc90cd7fab95a03412.png&h=0bb0db1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/111813_5980e8e0cbf610d0986aebf78ce1df27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F111813_5980e8e0cbf610d0986aebf78ce1df27.png&h=752ee817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/02/111815_f8c9d04b728a3d441ce9b20c32994f18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F02%2F111815_f8c9d04b728a3d441ce9b20c32994f18.png&h=f2ab9258&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b0d1ff4808d7c98ac4fc9f183e47de728ce683e","tid":1043036,"uid":224533,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:21:54.000Z","msg":"何廣沛個樣唔係咁啱操大隻"},{"pid":"42a104f69b9d86285ead03900a2a8f8387e9393e","tid":1043036,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"佢喺邊間做"},{"pid":"31535e33c1133ce23feeb5df46318960727b4580","tid":1043036,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42a104f69b9d86285ead03900a2a8f8387e9393e","tid":1043036,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"佢喺邊間做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:25:55.000Z","msg":"Goji"},{"pid":"8fba8229712fdb114308c82bcfebc525cf2c4764","tid":1043036,"uid":833,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T03:33:43.000Z","msg":"最尾果張圖<br />\n<br />\n舉